items.sentence: Tom was the only one on his boat when it sank.
Tom was the only person who needed to do that.
Tom was the one who told me we should do that.
It turns out we didn't need to do that anyway.
Tom was the only person who wanted to do that.
Tom was the one that Mary went to Boston with.
Tom's father often takes Tom fishing with him.
Tom went to great lengths to cover his tracks.
Tom spent most of the morning waiting in line.
Tom spent three months in Australia last year.
